  <name>Touché</name>
  <summary>Multi-touch Gestures</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Easily configure your touchpad and touchscreen multi-touch gestures with this GTK graphical user interface.</p>
    <p>For example, you can swipe up with 3 fingers to maximize a window or swipe left with 4 finger to switch to the next desktop.</p>
    <p>There are many more actions and gestures available and everything is easily configurable.</p>
    <p>Touchégg must also be installed:</p>
    <p>https://github.com/JoseExposito/touchegg#readme</p>
  </description>
